## verification

- [ ] all approved lessons have matched briefs
- [ ] brief names follow convention: `rule.*.md`, `howto.*.md`, `handoff.*.md`
- [ ] each brief has `.what`, `.why`, and `.source` sections
- [ ] commits reference cicd.deflake reflection as source
- [ ] handoffs include actionable next steps

